abstract: Plane crashes in New Delhi, killing all 10 people on board.
lead_paragraph: An aircraft carrying a team of technicians from India’s Border Security Force burst into flames after crashing near an airport boundary wall, killing all on board.

headline.main: Crash Near New Delhi Airport Leaves 10 Dead
headline.print_headline: World Briefing | Asia; India: Plane Crash Leaves 10 Dead
